body:
It looks like `org.apache.beam.sdk.transforms.CombineTest.testSessionsCombineWithContext` is flaky and sometimes passes and sometimes fails on not enough successful assertions.
This could either be an issue with the code it tests, or it could be an issue with the counters themselves that they are overcounting in some cases and that causes us to have incorrect test successes in this and other tests.

@aljoscha can you PTAL?
